---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import InlinePill from "../components/InlinePill.astro";
import profileImage from "../assets/me-again.jpg";
---

<Layout title="About - Steve Whitfield">
  <main>
    <!-- Profile Section -->
    <div class="border-t border-dashed border-gray-200">
      <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto border-x border-gray-200 px-6 py-8">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <img
              src={profileImage.src}
              alt="Steve Whitfield"
              class="w-40 h-40 object-cover border border-gray-200"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1 text-lg text-gray-700 leading-[2]">
            <p class="mb-4">
              Hello, I'm Steve — Father of two & co-founder of <InlinePill
                href="https://ludi.co"
                icon="image"
                iconSrc="https://ludi.co/favicon.ico">Ludi.co</InlinePill
              >. I'm 38 years old. My favourite color is <InlinePill
                href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Teal"
                icon="color"
                iconColor="bg-teal-500">teal</InlinePill
              > and my favourite dinosaur is <InlinePill
                href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ankylosaurus"
                icon="emoji"
                iconEmoji="🦕">Ankylosaurus</InlinePill
              >.
            </p>
            <p class="mb-4">
              As a (once) solo founder I'm well versed in every part of software delivery, from design to dev-ops and everything in between.
            </p>
            <p class="mb-4"> I pretend to support
              <InlinePill
                href="https://www.cpfc.co.uk/"
                icon="emoji"
                iconEmoji="⚽">
                Crystal Palace FC
              </InlinePill>
              but really I don't care about football.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>

    <!-- Life Story Section -->
    <div class="border-t border-dashed border-gray-200">
      <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto border-x border-gray-200 px-6 py-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">My Life Story</h2>

        <div class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-[2]">
          <p class="mb-4">
            I was born on 20th August 1987 in Rotherham, South Yorkshire.
            Rotherham is very nice, you should go.
          </p>
          <p class="mb-4">
            On my 3rd birthday I ran away from my parents and their friends
            singing Happy Birthday to me and locked myself in my grandparents
            caravan.
          </p>
          <p class="mb-4">
            As a child I enjoyed sailing, computer games and the usual kids stuff.
          </p>
          <p class="mb-4">
            I didn't really enjoy school, and ended leaving with average grades
            and average memories.
          </p>
          <p class="mb-4">
            I attended Nottingham Trent University, completed a placement at
            Hewlett Packard in Germany, and graduated with a 1st class degree in
            Software Engineering. Overall, university was good.
          </p>
          <p class="mb-4">
            From 2009 to 2016, I worked the following jobs:
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="overflow-x-auto">
          <table
            class="min-w-full text-gray-700 text-left"
          >
            <thead class="bg-accent-500 text-white">
              <tr>
                <th class="py-2 px-3 font-semibold">Dates</th>
                <th class="py-2 px-3 font-semibold">Company</th>
                <th class="py-2 px-3 font-semibold">Role</th>
                <th class="py-2 px-3 font-semibold">Notes</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody class="border border-gray-200 border-t-0">
              <tr class="odd:bg-gray-50 even:bg-white hover:bg-gray-100 transition">
                <td class="py-2 px-3">2009–2010</td>
                <td class="py-2 px-3">Esendex</td>
                <td class="py-2 px-3">Junior Developer</td>
                <td class="py-2 px-3">Decent</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="odd:bg-gray-50 even:bg-white hover:bg-gray-100 transition">
                <td class="py-2 px-3">2010–2011</td>
                <td class="py-2 px-3">Omnifone</td>
                <td class="py-2 px-3">Software Developer</td>
                <td class="py-2 px-3">Chaos (bad kind)</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="odd:bg-gray-50 even:bg-white hover:bg-gray-100 transition">
                <td class="py-2 px-3">2011</td>
                <td class="py-2 px-3">TTT Money Corporation</td>
                <td class="py-2 px-3">Software Developer</td>
                <td class="py-2 px-3">Awful</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="odd:bg-gray-50 even:bg-white hover:bg-gray-100 transition">
                <td class="py-2 px-3">2011–2014</td>
                <td class="py-2 px-3">Crab Creative</td>
                <td class="py-2 px-3">Web Developer</td>
                <td class="py-2 px-3">Chaos (good kind)</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="odd:bg-gray-50 even:bg-white hover:bg-gray-100 transition">
                <td class="py-2 px-3">2014–2016</td>
                <td class="py-2 px-3">Chelsea Apps</td>
                <td class="py-2 px-3">Software Engineer & Tech Lead</td>
                <td class="py-2 px-3">Lucrative</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
        <div class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-[2] mt-6">
          <p class="mb-4">
            In 2016, myself and 4 others left Chelsea Apps and took our Large
            Global Accounting Firm client with us. We setup our own consultancy
            and were paid handsomley for our work from 2016 until 2019.
          </p>
          <p class="mb-4">
            In 2017 I get engaged to the love of my life.
          </p>
          <p class="mb-4">
            In early 2019, we wound up the consultancy and, later on that year, I
            launched the first version of Metro Retro.
          </p>
          <p class="mb-4">
            Later in 2019 my son was born.
          </p>
          <p class="mb-4">
            The following year Covid-19 caused the popularity of Metro Retro to
            skyrocket. Jamie Hanratty joins as our co-founder.
          </p>
          <p class="mb-4">
            Two years later (which is WAY too long), Metro Retro took it's first
            paying customers.
          </p>
          <p class="mb-4">
            After scrapping for another two years, Metro Retro joins TinySeed.
          </p>
          <p class="mb-4">
            In 2025, Metro Retro rebrands as Ludi.co
          </p>
          <p class="mb-4">
            Also in 2025, I decide to make a personal website, I'll let you know
            how it turns out.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
